===Suffix===
{{head|ga|suffix}}

# {{non-gloss definition|emphatic suffix of the third-person singular masculine; used after velarized consonants and back vowels}}
# {{non-gloss definition|emphatic suffix of the third-person plural; used after velarized consonants and back vowels}}

====Usage notes====
Spelled with a hyphen after ''-s'', otherwise without a hyphen.
* Added to [[noun]]s (or [[adjective]]s modifying a noun) in the presence of the [[possessive adjective]] to emphasize the possessor rather than the thing possessed:
*: {{ux|ga|a mhadra'''san'''|''his'' dog|inline=1}}
*: {{ux|ga|a gcarr dearg'''san'''|''their'' red car|inline=1}}
* Added to [[pronoun]]s (both simple and prepositional) to add emphasis (''not'' to create a reflexive pronoun):
*: {{ux|ga|as'''-san'''|out of ''him''|inline=1}}
*: {{ux|ga|siad'''san''', iad'''san'''|''they'', ''them''|inline=1}}
* Added to synthetic [[verb]] forms to add emphasis to the subject (third-person plural only as there are no third-person singular synthetic forms):
*: {{ux|ga|chualadar'''san'''|''they'' heard|inline=1}}

